trans-unit.source: Specifies the code-beside handler information in the <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.BeforeHandlerInvoked(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor)" /> and <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.UpdateHandlerMethodsForActivity(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Collections.Generic.List{System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor})" /> methods.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.BeforeHandlerInvoked(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor)" /> 和 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.UpdateHandlerMethodsForActivity(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Collections.Generic.List{System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor})" /> 方法中指定 Code-Beside 處理常式資訊。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> representing the name of the handler method.
trans-unit.target: 代表處理常式方法名稱的 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> representing the CLR metadata token identifier for the handler method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" />，代表處理常式方法的 CLR 中繼資料語彙基元識別項。
